Package: EconCausal
Title: Econometric Methods for Causal Inference with Temporal Stability
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("José Mauricio", "Gómez Julián", email = "isadore.nabi@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements three complementary methodologies for causal inference in economic time series with emphasis on temporal stability: Bayesian GLM with AR(1), ECM-MARS, and Bayesian Structural Time Series.
License: MIT
